==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Broadseal
<hw>Broad"seal`</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To stamp with the broad
seal; to make sure; to guarantee or warrant.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thy presence <qex>broadseals</qex> our delights for pure.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>broad-shouldered</ent>⟦br⟧
